{"tid":405052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【會考Loser，奶共Winner】李國章會考理科僅合格","createTime":"2017-09-18T14:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T00:53:13.000Z","uid":11001,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4a228d384635ce4b31c89a88a8b0a2e800284d","tid":405052,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"近期削減大學撥款滿城風雨，主角之一嘅李國章被學生批評不願對話兼耍太極，但原來中學時代的李沙皇又主動又活躍。佢母校聖保羅男女中學六一年嘅同學錄，仲以「上堂好作妙語，為班房內增加情趣不少」來形容佢。校刊仲載有李局長一篇英文文章，講番佢嘅中五畢業晚宴盛況，會考英文科攞火箭嘅李局長，當然有番咁上下文采。<span style=\"color: red;\">但最估唔到，呢位劍橋醫科博士，當年會考時生、理、化三科成績只係合格，局長一定花咗唔少心機先做到大國手。</span>今次削資風波與亞瑟王打對台嘅理大校長潘宗光，原來係李局長嘅師兄。潘校長曾經自己講因為家境不佳，中學時得班主任岑老師同校長羅怡基鼓勵與支持，發奮向學而獲減免學費，才得以繼續升學。除咗佢哋兩位，聖保羅男女仲有唔少猛人，好似周梁淑怡、法律界嘅余若薇同李國能，考評局委員會主席顧爾言等，認真人才輩出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.next.nextmedia.com/article/715/3671469\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.next.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F715%2F3671469&d=H%2Fo8OJ15tEGH5c9q5LS%2BDjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0055eb8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.next.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F715%2F3671469&h=36eb3d21\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.next.nextmedia.com/article/715/3671469</a>"},{"pid":"ae60f4aa5fa1d4c310b776d83590cc96f5813f9b","tid":405052,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d32b926e3ca51d6502a8006bb7d15c9f4bd997","tid":405052,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583c6a1a26794f564d657077dc7fe8dbf73d4f04","tid":405052,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fd1f7ff7ea9fe6bc435119109c74d0603489f3","tid":405052,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":